Package: com.jcatalog.wiki.block

[Java] Class ParagraphBlock

        • com.jcatalog.wiki.block.ParagraphBlock

        • Class is the same as net.java.textilej.parser.markup.confluence.block.ParagraphBlock, except 'confluenceBlockStart' constant value, because processing for {code}, {info}, {tip}, {warning}, {panel}, {note} and {toc} blocks don't needed.
